<speak version="1.0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis" xmlns:mstts="https://www.w3.org/2001/mstts" xml:lang="en-IN">
  <voice name="en-IN-Diya:DragonHDLatestNeural">
    <break time="700ms"/>
    <prosody rate="-12%" pitch="-2st" volume="soft">This first segment tests low, soothing prosody independently.</prosody>
    <break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="whispering" styledegree="1.4">This is the Dragon HD whispering style test.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="calm" styledegree="0.85">This is the calm style test.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="curious" styledegree="1.1">What changes when the assumption moves?</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="reflective" styledegree="1.05">Pause and consider what the number leaves out.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="encouraging" styledegree="1.1">Good. Now trace the cash flow one step further.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="serious" styledegree="1.15">A rating is not a substitute for evidence.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="concerned" styledegree="1.1">The structure becomes fragile when the reserve is depleted.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="skeptical" styledegree="1.15">What would make this conclusion fail?</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="impressed" styledegree="1">Now the transaction begins to make sense.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="surprised" styledegree="1.15">The same cash flow can protect one tranche and threaten another.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="joking" styledegree="1">The formula is not the explanation.</mstts:express-as>
<break time="650ms"/><mstts:express-as style="laughing" styledegree="1">That is the part people often overlook.</mstts:express-as>
    <break time="650ms"/>
    [laughter]
    <break time="450ms"/>
    [sighing]
    <break time="450ms"/>
    [breathing]
    <break time="450ms"/>
    [throat_clearing]
  </voice>
